      <title>特朗普的社交媒体公司定于周二在纳斯达克交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/trump-s-social-media-company-set-to-trade-tuesday-on-nasdaq</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家空白支票公司与前总统唐纳德·特朗普的社交媒体初创公司合并后，合并后的公司宣布将于周二开始交易，这家公司的股价周一飙升了 35%，这可能会给他带来一笔意外之财。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/trump-s-social-media-company-set-to-trade-tuesday-on-nasdaq</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 16:13:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车制造商竞相自救，菲斯克被纽约证券交易所摘牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/fisker-fsr-talks-with-automaker-end-raising-risk-of-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约证券交易所周一宣布，在电动汽车初创公司菲斯克公司(Fisker Inc.)不会获得大型汽车制造商投资的消息传出后，该公司股价下跌，该​​公司将暂停其股票交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/fisker-fsr-talks-with-automaker-end-raising-risk-of-bankruptcy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 13:59:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高额拖欠率给巴西金融科技公司带来麻烦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/delinquencies-topping-60-spell-trouble-for-brazil-s-fintechs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西金融科技公司正遭受一波贷款违约潮的打击，这些贷款是巴西规模较大的传统银行不愿接触的客户贷款，导致资产支持信贷市场的风险层崩溃。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/delinquencies-topping-60-spell-trouble-for-brazil-s-fintechs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
